  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Objective and critical voices are under attack from increasingly polarizing politics, uncivil discourse in mainstream media and a digital culture easy to manipulate. This project allows donors to contribute to RNTC&apos;s Scholarship Fund to be used to train young, critically minded media professionals (journalists, bloggers, vloggers) worldwide, so they can act as guardians of public interest. With 50 years of experience, RNTC trains professionals worldwide in the use of media for social change.</narrative>
  </description>
